    "updated_at": "2026-05-14T04:53:50Z",
    "body": "Reproduced — confirmed root cause. The langchain-openai converters preserve `reasoning_content` in the *response* direction (response → AIMessage at `converters/completions.ts:276-298` and streaming delta at `:419-420`), but the reverse path (`convertMessagesToCompletionsMessageParams` / `convertStandardContentMessageToCompletionsMessage`) never re-emits it on the outbound request, so DeepSeek rejects the follow-up turn with a 400. ChatDeepSeek extends ChatOpenAICompletions so it goes through the same path. Will put up a fix shortly.",
